## ğŸ¯ Overview

**StudyMateAI** is a production-ready, enterprise-grade learning management platform that revolutionizes the study experience by combining cutting-edge web technologies with artificial intelligence. Built with scalability and performance in mind, it delivers real-time communication, automated intelligent notifications, and AI-powered document analysis to create the ultimate study companion.

### âœ¨ Key Features

#### ğŸ¤– AI-Powered Intelligence

- **Advanced Chat Assistant** - Powered by Groq's llama-3.3-70b-versatile model for intelligent, context-aware responses
- **Document Q&A** - Chat directly with your PDF study materials using AI-powered text extraction
- **Smart Recommendations** - Personalized study suggestions based on your progress and patterns

#### ğŸ“š Learning Management

- **Subject & Course Organization** - Hierarchical structure for all your academic materials
- **PDF Document Management** - Upload, categorize, and manage study resources with metadata tagging
- **Progress Tracking** - Visual analytics dashboard to monitor your learning journey

#### ğŸ“… Smart Scheduling

- **Intelligent Calendar** - Track exams, assignments, and study sessions with color-coded organization
- **Automated Reminders** - Cron-based notifications at 7 days, 3 days, 1 day, and day-of events
- **Countdown Timers** - Real-time tracking of upcoming deadlines

#### ğŸ”” Real-Time Communication

- **WebSocket Notifications** - Instant alerts for important events and updates
- **Notification Center** - Unified inbox with read/unread status and filtering
- **Priority Levels** - Categorized alerts (urgent, warning, info)

#### ğŸ¨ Modern User Experience

- **Futuristic Dark UI** - Premium glassmorphism design with smooth animations
- **Fully Responsive** - Optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- **Accessibility First** - WCAG compliant with keyboard navigation support

#### ğŸ” Enterprise Security

- **JWT Authentication** - Secure token-based authentication with refresh tokens
- **Role-Based Access Control** - Granular permissions for different user types
- **Data Encryption** - Password hashing with bcrypt and secure data transmission

## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture

### Technology Stack

<div align="center">

| Layer             | Technologies                                        |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Frontend**      | Angular 19, TypeScript, RxJS, Signals, Tailwind CSS |
| **Backend**       | NestJS, Node.js, TypeScript, TypeORM                |
| **Database**      | PostgreSQL, InfluxDB (IoT features)                 |
| **AI/ML**         | Groq API (llama-3.3-70b-versatile), pdf2json        |
| **Real-Time**     | WebSockets, NestJS Schedule (Cron)                  |
| **DevOps**        | Docker, Docker Compose, pgAdmin                     |
| **Security**      | JWT, bcrypt, CORS, class-validator                  |
| **Documentation** | Swagger/OpenAPI                                     |

</div>

